			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load CTY_Main_A\r\nGo to steel watch foundry\r\nGet at least one stone through the debug book (Emperor Prelude)\r\nDrop at least one inside the steel watch foundry building\r\nSetGlobalOsirisFlag IRN_IronThrone_State_Destroyed\r\nWalk to the Looters (should see Netherstone icons on map)\r\nKill them\r\nLoot the stones"
				},
